    "---\n",
    "## 🏥 Caso 2: Salud — Predicción de Readmisión Hospitalaria\n",
    "\n",
    "**Contexto:** Hospital universitario necesita predecir qué pacientes tienen >30% de probabilidad de ser readmitidos en los próximos 30 días, para intervención preventiva.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Técnicas:** NumPy para álgebra lineal, SVD para reducción dimensional de datos clínicos."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ── Dataset clínico sintético ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
    "np.random.seed(2024)\n",
    "n_pacientes = 1000\n",
    "\n",
    "# Features clínicas (normalizadas internamente)\n",
    "# [edad, dias_hospitalizacion, n_comorbilidades, n_medicamentos,\n",
    "#  presion_sistolica, hemoglobina, creatinina, albumina,\n",
    "#  n_visitas_urgencias_6m, indice_charlson]\n",
    "FEATURE_NAMES = [\n",
    "    \"edad\", \"dias_hosp\", \"n_comorbilidades\", \"n_medicamentos\",\n",
    "    \"presion_sistolica\", \"hemoglobina\", \"creatinina\",\n",
    "    \"albumina\", \"visitas_urgencias\", \"charlson_idx\"\n",
    "]\n",
    "\n",
    "# Grupos de riesgo\n",
    "bajo_riesgo  = np.random.multivariate_normal(\n",
    "    mean=[55, 4, 1, 3, 125, 13, 0.9, 3.8, 0, 1],\n",
    "    cov=np.diag([100, 4, 0.5, 2, 200, 4, 0.1, 0.3, 0.5, 1]),\n",
    "    size=600\n",
    ")\n",
    "alto_riesgo  = np.random.multivariate_normal(\n",
    "    mean=[72, 10, 4, 8, 155, 10, 2.1, 2.8, 3, 5],\n",
    "    cov=np.diag([150, 9, 2, 4, 300, 6, 0.5, 0.4, 1, 2]),\n",
    "    size=400\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "X_clinico = np.vstack([bajo_riesgo, alto_riesgo])\n",
    "y_readmision = np.hstack([np.zeros(600), np.ones(400)])\n",
    "\n",
    "# Shuffle\n",
    "idx = np.random.permutation(n_pacientes)\n",
    "X_clinico = X_clinico[idx]\n",
    "y_readmision = y_readmision[idx]\n",
    "\n",
    "# ── Análisis PCA manual con SVD ───────────────────────────────────────────\n",
    "# Estandarizar\n",
    "mu    = X_clinico.mean(axis=0)\n",
    "sigma = X_clinico.std(axis=0) + 1e-8\n",
    "X_std = (X_clinico - mu) / sigma\n",
    "\n",
    "#